&gt; the exceptions; 
&gt; log and rethrow them.  If you want to do this to
&gt; *all* your tests, 
&gt; then create an abstract base class that extends
&gt; TestCase, containing 
&gt; your version of this method, and extend all your
&gt; test classes from 
